  "body": "# Problem\n\nKeycards are being wiped on recoveryâ€”we are therefore not going to sell any until we have resolved the issue. \n\nThis issue is to hide any Keycard related options in the onboarding & recovery flows on Android. Keycard options are already hidden on iOS.\n\n## Implementation\n\nRemove these options from Android v1 build:\n - Unlock screen -> Add existing keys -> `Recover with Keycard`\n- During onboarding (Access existing keys -> Enter seedphrase  --> ..... -> Select Keycard as storage)\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15470435/71670637-81600f80-2d3e-11ea-949a-a59fa51c305c.png)\n\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\nOption to recovery with Keycard no longer appears on Android.\nKey storage selection no longer appears on Android during onboarding.\n\n## Notes\n\ncc @guylouis @gravityblast @andremedeiros \n\n## Future Steps\n\nResolve erased keycard issue w/ help of NXP.",
